Package interfaces.dao

package interfaces.dao
The interfaces.dao package contains interfaces that define data access operations.

Interfaces in this package provide a contract for classes that are responsible for interacting with the underlying data storage mechanisms. These interfaces define common methods for creating, reading, updating, and deleting data entities.

Classes that implement these interfaces typically handle the low-level details of data storage, such as database queries, file I/O, or communication with external services.
